data.description: Charming 4-bedroom cul-de-sac home seeks a new family! Note that one of the bedrooms is a flex room (great for an office or den) since it doesn't have a closet, but don't worry, the tax rolls are aware and show 3 bedrooms. The home has double pane windows, AC, and newer roof. The primary bedroom is spacious offering a bathroom that's fresh retreat, boasting a walk-in shower offers a seat with a high-tech exhaust fan featuring Bluetooth, mood lighting for those spa-like vibes. The Carrera marble vanity brings the brightness throughout the bathroom. The guest bath? Totally updated. Kitchen has a window that overlooks the backyard to keep an eye on the kiddos. The living room offers a fireplace with sliding door that opens to the backyard with enough space to add an ADU, complete with a separate entrance on Orange. Perfect for extra income or visiting family!
